<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.5.9">
<l>kaṉañcey māmatiḷ kaṇapurat tavaṉoṭuṅ kaṉaviṉi lavaṉtanta</l>
<l>maṉañce yiṉpamvan tuṭpuka veḷkiyeṉ vaḷaineka viruntēṉai</l>
<l>ciṉañcey mālviṭaic ciṟumaṇi yōcaiyeṉ cintaiyaic cintuvikkum</l>
<l>aṉanta laṉṟili ṉarikural pāviyē ṉāviyai yaṭukiṉṟatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The sound of the little bells on the dark bulls which clash</l>
<l rend="indent">shatters my thoughts, me who waited as my bangles slipped,</l>
<l>Being troubled since the mind-made delight which he gave me in a dream</l>
<l>Of him of Kaṇṇapuram, with thickly-made great walls,</l>
<l rend="indent">came and obsessed [me].</l>
<l>The cutting call of the dozing black ibis, wretched me, is destroying my soul.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
